    Let unsigned_value be clamped_value
    If unsigned_value is less than 0:
        Set unsigned_value to unsigned_value plus 16777216  Note: 2^24
    
    Note: Extract bytes in little-endian order
    Let byte0 be unsigned_value modulo 256
    Let byte1 be (unsigned_value divided by 256) modulo 256
    Let byte2 be (unsigned_value divided by 65536) modulo 256
    
    Try:
        Return list containing:
            system_call_integer_to_hex_string with value as byte0 and padding as 2
            system_call_integer_to_hex_string with value as byte1 and padding as 2
